name: com.virnect.track
description:
VIRNECT Track

Track is a cross-platform augmented reality framework.
With this package, you can easily integrate cutting-edge computer vision technologies into your AR projects.

Track is able to track multiple different target types:
▪ Images
▪ QR-Codes
▪ 3D Objects
▪ CAD Models
▪ MAP Targets
▪ Shape Targets 

Track also supports: 
▪Fusion tracking with AR Foundation package
▪URP (Universial Rendering Pipeline)

 Please refer to the official documentation for details.
